OL,3,CChurch leadership say Bishop of
OL,4,CLiverpool 'will need to step aside'
OL,6,FThe statement continued: "We believe
OL,7,Fthat the allegations made by the
OL,8,Ffemale bishop need to be fully and
OL,9,Fproperly investigated.
OL,11,F"We also believe that while these
OL,12,Fproper investigations are conducted
OL,13,Fthe Bishop of Liverpool will need to
OL,14,Fstep aside from all ministry in the
OL,15,FDiocese of Liverpool."
OL,17,FBishop Perumbalath said he has
OL,18,F"consistently denied" the allegations
OL,19,Fand complied with any investigation
OL,20,Ffrom the National Safeguarding Team
OL,21,F(NST).
