OL,6,F"I have consistently denied the
OL,7,Fallegations made against me by both
OL,8,Fcomplainants. I have complied with any
OL,9,Finvestigation from the National
OL,10,FSafeguarding Team.
OL,12,F"The allegations raised in Essex were
OL,13,Falso investigated by the police who
OL,14,Ftook no further action.
OL,16,F"Whilst I don't believe I have done
OL,17,Fanything wrong, I have taken seriously
OL,18,Fthe lessons learned through this
OL,19,Fprocess addressing how my actions can
OL,20,Fbe perceived by others.
